  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Open CRM in the left rail.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 1.788,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "The sidebar stacks every kind of customer record: members, gift cards, house accounts,",
      "startS": 2.504,
      "endS": 5.042,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "and the four we cover today.",
      "startS": 5.38,
      "endS": 9.089,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "One page per record type.",
      "startS": 9.772,
      "endS": 11.215,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "Learn where each one lives and you stop guessing which screen holds the answer.",
      "startS": 11.806,
      "endS": 15.593,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "Click Prepaid Books.",
      "startS": 16,
      "endS": 17.392,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "A prepaid book is a stack of washes a customer already paid for.",
      "startS": 17.896,
      "endS": 21.63,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "The tiles up top count them: total, active, completed, and how many expire soon.",
      "startS": 22.201,
      "endS": 23.725,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "In today's capture those numbers were still loading,",
      "startS": 24.201,
      "endS": 27.965,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "but the labels tell you exactly what to read.",
      "startS": 28.699,
      "endS": 33.92,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Now the list itself.",
      "startS": 34.32,
      "endS": 35.608,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Six columns, and two do the work on a call:",
      "startS": 36.643,
      "endS": 39.382,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "Remaining tells you washes left, Expiration tells you the deadline.",
      "startS": 40.053,
      "endS": 41.932,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "The rows failed to load in this capture,",
      "startS": 42.424,
      "endS": 44.282,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "so read the column headers and refresh live before you promise a customer anything.",
      "startS": 45.116,
      "endS": 51.765,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "Click Vehicles.",
      "startS": 52.306,
      "endS": 53.685,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "This is the master plate list, nearly four thousand cars.",
      "startS": 54.176,
      "endS": 57.634,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "The tiles loaded here: total vehicles, active members, flagged, and new this month.",
      "startS": 57.931,
      "endS": 59.093,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "When a plate gets flagged at the gate, Flagged is your first stop.",
      "startS": 59.606,
      "endS": 67.36,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "Scroll to the list.",
      "startS": 67.831,
      "endS": 68.821,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "Seven columns: plate, make and model, year, customer, location, status, last visit.",
      "startS": 69.32,
      "endS": 70.862,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "For a dispute you want License Plate and Status.",
      "startS": 71.304,
      "endS": 72.133,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "The rows hit the same fetch error, but the tiles above prove the data is there.",
      "startS": 72.451,
      "endS": 72.944,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "It just didn't stream into the table.",
      "startS": 73.484,
      "endS": 86.925,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "Click Retail Customers.",
      "startS": 87.52,
      "endS": 89.031,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "This one is bare on purpose.",
      "startS": 89.993,
      "endS": 91.853,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "No tiles, no charts, just a search box and five columns:",
      "startS": 92.168,
      "endS": 96.509,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "customer, plate, home location, email, phone.",
      "startS": 96.932,
      "endS": 100.465,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "It holds walk-ins and non-members, the people without a full membership record.",
      "startS": 101.22,
      "endS": 105.464,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "Search, read the contact, done.",
      "startS": 106.237,
      "endS": 108.479,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "Click Bundles.",
      "startS": 108.88,
      "endS": 109.884,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "A bundle is a packaged deal a site sells.",
      "startS": 110.452,
      "endS": 113.076,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "The tiles loaded: thirty-two bundles, twenty-eight active, and this month's sales and revenue.",
      "startS": 113.368,
      "endS": 114.423,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "The Revenue by Bundle panel ranks which packages actually move,",
      "startS": 114.815,
      "endS": 119.023,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "so you can see the Monthly Value Pack carrying the month.",
      "startS": 119.606,
      "endS": 126.561,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "Now the list, and this one actually loaded.",
      "startS": 127.094,
      "endS": 127.864,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Seven columns, and five packages on screen,",
      "startS": 128.121,
      "endS": 129.487,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "from the Summer Special to the Fleet Pack built for fleets.",
      "startS": 129.8,
      "endS": 135.592,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "Watch the Valid At column: some run at every site, others only at a couple.",
      "startS": 136.236,
      "endS": 140.65,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "That column settles most \"does this work at my location\" questions.",
      "startS": 141.121,
      "endS": 144.851,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "One more entry, Fundraiser, sits right below Bundles.",
      "startS": 145.28,
      "endS": 147.802,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "Do not click it.",
      "startS": 147.802,
      "endS": 149.313,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "Its link goes nowhere and the page was never built.",
      "startS": 149.313,
      "endS": 152.822,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "It is parked, so treat the menu item as a placeholder",
      "startS": 152.822,
      "endS": 156.692,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "and never promise a customer a fundraiser feature from this screen.",
      "startS": 156.692,
      "endS": 160.16,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "So, four lists, one sidebar.",
      "startS": 160.56,
      "endS": 162.88,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "Prepaid Books for washes left and expiry.",
      "startS": 163.424,
      "endS": 166.143,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "Vehicles for plates and flags.",
      "startS": 166.449,
      "endS": 168.147,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "Retail Customers for walk-ins.",
      "startS": 168.367,
      "endS": 170.484,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "Bundles for what's on the menu and where.",
      "startS": 170.846,
      "endS": 172.947,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "Match the ticket to the list, open it, read the row.",
      "startS": 173.415,
      "endS": 175.008,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "That's the whole job on these four screens.",
      "startS": 175.245,
      "endS": 179.2,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}